title: Bill Plaschke's Wakeup Call: Dodgers are out... again
text:
Bill Plaschke Bill Plaschke's Wakeup Call: Dodgers are out... again 
The Dodgers ended their season the same way they've ended it the two before: losing in the playoffs. L.A. Times sports columnist Bill Plaschke laments the early exit and wonders where they go next.
